Package it.unimore.iot.health.api.datamanager.dto

Class PatientUpdateRequest

java.lang.Object
it.unimore.iot.health.api.datamanager.dto.PatientUpdateRequest
public class PatientUpdateRequest extends Object
PatientUpdateRequest is a DTO class (Data Transfer Object) that allows clients to only have access to certain attributes when updating a patient. It allows them to modify DTO class' attributes, while the other attributes of the PatientDescriptor are not accessible (the server replies with 400 Bad Request "Unable to process JSON")
Author:
Christopher Zanoli, Undergraduate student - 270765@studenti.unimore.it
